title: Combined update for contrib/go
body_html:
This PR merges 1700+ commits from master into go.

Currently working in this fork.

Changes:

  • Minor syntax alterations to the public C api header.
  • Where merge conflicts occur, code from master used exclusively.

Tests:

  • go test in tensorflow/contrib/go passes.
  • Inception model image recognition (from examples) works as expected.
  • pip3 build, installation, 'hello world' works as expected.

body:
This PR merges 1700+ commits from `master` into `go`. 

Currently working [in this fork](https://github.com/damienstanton/tensorflow/tree/go).

Changes: 
- Minor syntax alterations to the public C api header. 
- Where merge conflicts occur, code from `master` used exclusively.

Tests:
- [X] `go test` in tensorflow/contrib/go passes.
- [X] Inception model image recognition ([from examples](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/go/tensorflow/g3doc/tutorials/image_recognition/index.md#usage-with-the-go-api)) works as expected.
- [X] `pip3` build, installation, 'hello world' works as expected.
